    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/ac84532d9b4f9b0d6597a57fcd2575fd.poster.avif?t=1772121592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/ac84532d9b4f9b0d6597a57fcd2575fd.webm?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/ac84532d9b4f9b0d6597a57fcd2575fd.mp4?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/04b3df89fbc033afcc2354656265457a.webp?t=1772121592\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead nomadic families through the Stone Age in this turn-based 4X strategy game with deeply simulated characters, cultures, and ecosystems. Explore the vast wilderness, gather and trade scarce resources, and stand your ground in risky autobattler combat. Discover fire, domestication, politics—and survive to tell the tale.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience what prehistoric life was like by diving into this exploration of ecology, paleolithic societies, and the origins of culture. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/ebe32019c9e006076ad000601bf8e26e.webp?t=1772121592\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/602b3bb87b1e817535cb1b37030796e4.poster.avif?t=1772121592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/602b3bb87b1e817535cb1b37030796e4.webm?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/602b3bb87b1e817535cb1b37030796e4.mp4?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before agriculture and settlements, we spent hundreds of thousands of years as nomadic hunter-gatherers. Guide your people as you migrate through harsh climates, each posing unique challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/3461079c32aad6a939186e485d4e3beb.webp?t=1772121592\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/da46594196cbca54f7f30d1245800d5c.poster.avif?t=1772121592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/da46594196cbca54f7f30d1245800d5c.webm?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/da46594196cbca54f7f30d1245800d5c.mp4?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage the relationships between individuals, families, and tribes. Watch your collective adapt over countless generations. Beware the unintended consequences current choices can have on your great-great-great-grandchildren. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/a44f59813a2cf3aefc01818e134550df.webp?t=1772121592\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/78a9f6e7ea9e41a7f0452454f8fbea0b.poster.avif?t=1772121592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/78a9f6e7ea9e41a7f0452454f8fbea0b.webm?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/78a9f6e7ea9e41a7f0452454f8fbea0b.mp4?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize your strategy before each autobattler skirmish, because a warrior is not just a warrior. When one falls in combat, the tribe loses not only a fighter but also a skilled hunter, family member, and carrier of hard-won wisdom passed down through the ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/c751d802c7d8d901c3bf6a4b724d7f64.webp?t=1772121592\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/046d5df6588228020ec18201654c5968.poster.avif?t=1772121592\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/046d5df6588228020ec18201654c5968.webm?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/046d5df6588228020ec18201654c5968.mp4?t=1772121592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt, gather, and extract resources from the ecosystems around you, but tread carefully: nature is ruthless and you are at its mercy. Maintain the natural equilibrium or face sudden and unexpected challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275300/extras/d8239ac50b85715cf437b0264e4e1bee.avif?t=1772121592\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Technology: a tech tree spanning the Pleistocene up to the start of the Bronze Age, covering skills from controlled fire and cooking, through domestication and agriculture, all the way to megalithic construction and the first cities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Culture: shape your tribe’s unique culture, with evolving cultural norms that differentiate you from your neighbors, affecting trade and war. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Economy: resources are finite and their extraction affects the environment. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ecology: 9 unique climates, each with a complex and dynamic food web. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated Earth-like maps based on realistic climate simulations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many generations of deeply simulated individuals with heritable traits, all affecting various game systems. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Narrative events that can alter the trajectory of your entire tribe. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Social Networks: Dynamic social network visualization, enabling a new way to understand and manage family trees and relationships between members of your band. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diplomacy: trade, fight, or collaborate with other tribes.</p></li></ul>",
